<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM10.4">
<l>mullaip pirāṭṭi nīyuṉ muṟuvalkaḷ koṇṭemmai</l>
<l>allal viḷaiviyē lāḻinaṅ kāyuṉ ṉaṭaikkalaṅ</l>
<l>kollai yarakkiyai mūkkarin tiṭṭa kumaraṉār</l>
<l>collumpoy yāṉāl, nāṉum piṟantamai poyyaṉṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O lady jasmine! Do not distress us with your smiles!</l>
<l>O deep lady! [I seek] your refuge.</l>
<l>If the words spoken by the young Man who cut off the transgressing rakshasi’s nose,</l>
<l>become untrue, my being born is also untrue, is it not?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
